{"font_size": 0.4, "font_color": "#FFFFFF", "background_alpha": 0.5, "background_color": "#9C27B0", "Stroke": "none", "body": [{"content": "「字幕由 富睿字幕组 搬运」", "from": 0, "location": 2, "to": 3}, {"content": "（HORI书店）", "from": 10.66, "location": 2, "to": 12.91}, {"content": "是这本吗", "from": 14.18, "location": 2, "to": 15.2}, {"content": "嗯 就是这个", "from": 17.41, "location": 2, "to": 18.99}, {"content": "谢谢了", "from": 19.36, "location": 2, "to": 20.27}, {"content": "不用谢", "from": 20.61, "location": 2, "to": 21.29}, {"content": "不知为何 我的眼睛能清晰地看到一些东西", "from": 25.4, "location": 2, "to": 29.51}, {"content": "很遗憾 并不是命中注定的恋人", "from": 30.23, "location": 2, "to": 33.3}, {"content": "应该是…", "from": 34.08, "location": 2, "to": 35.43}, {"content": "已死之人", "from": 36.45, "location": 2, "to": 37.67}, {"content": "你就是我的命运之人", "from": 40.83, "location": 2, "to": 43.08}, {"content": "你要摘下眼镜吗", "from": 45.66, "location": 2, "to": 47.16}, {"content": "明明眼睛不好", "from": 47.72, "location": 2, "to": 48.92}, {"content": "不 不好意思", "from": 54.95, "location": 2, "to": 56.7}, {"content": "三角（sankaku）？", "from": 57.08, "location": 2, "to": 58.36}, {"content": "是三角（mikado）", "from": 60.04, "location": 2, "to": 61.11}, {"content": "三角 没想到会碰巧遇到你…遇到你这样的人", "from": 61.59, "location": 2, "to": 66.92}, {"content": "这一定是命运", "from": 67.81, "location": 2, "to": 70.37}, {"content": "你的力量…", "from": 71.52, "location": 2, "to": 72.45}, {"content": "居然能看得这么清楚", "from": 72.9, "location": 2, "to": 75.01}, {"content": "抱歉这么突然", "from": 78.54, "location": 2, "to": 80.12}, {"content": "刚才那是什么", "from": 88.9, "location": 2, "to": 90.58}, {"content": "感觉非常地…", "from": 91.73, "location": 2, "to": 93.48}, {"content": "舒服", "from": 94.38, "location": 2, "to": 96.32}, {"content": "太棒了", "from": 98.98, "location": 2, "to": 100.37}, {"content": "原来命运是真的啊", "from": 100.84, "location": 2, "to": 102.54}, {"content": "原来幽灵是真的存在的啊", "from": 105.71, "location": 2, "to": 108.62}, {"content": "不过 冷川大师", "from": 108.84, "location": 2, "to": 110.68}, {"content": "除灵要怎么做啊", "from": 111.0, "location": 2, "to": 113.42}, {"content": "请不要叫我大师", "from": 113.52, "location": 2, "to": 115.51}, {"content": "就我个人来说 我的能力是抓住幽灵再扔掉", "from": 115.99, "location": 2, "to": 120.31}, {"content": "扔掉？", "from": 121.5, "location": 2, "to": 122.51}, {"content": "三角 你醒了？", "from": 123.34, "location": 2, "to": 124.85}, {"content": "我们店不是一直有传闻说有幽灵吗", "from": 125.28, "location": 2, "to": 129.96}, {"content": "还挺严重的", "from": 129.96, "location": 2, "to": 131.88}, {"content": "所以…", "from": 131.94, "location": 2, "to": 132.95}, {"content": "你要不要起来说话", "from": 133.52, "location": 2, "to": 134.89}, {"content": "我还是第一次晕倒 实在是起不来", "from": 135.53, "location": 2, "to": 140.51}, {"content": "舒服到晕倒了吗", "from": 140.92, "location": 2, "to": 143.26}, {"content": "那是我直接触碰了你的灵魂", "from": 144.69, "location": 2, "to": 148.29}, {"content": "以你为增幅器 把幽灵扔掉了", "from": 149.17, "location": 2, "to": 151.57}, {"content": "灵魂互相接触会很舒服", "from": 152.2, "location": 2, "to": 154.47}, {"content": "而且接触上之后我发现 我们俩的相性非常好", "from": 155.0, "location": 2, "to": 159.88}, {"content": "真是命运…", "from": 160.14, "location": 2, "to": 160.65}, {"content": "是骗人的吧", "from": 160.65, "location": 2, "to": 161.36}, {"content": "你要否定你看到的东西吗", "from": 165.6, "location": 2, "to": 169.34}, {"content": "三角 你有灵感的吗", "from": 169.57, "location": 2, "to": 171.96}, {"content": "为什么不说啊", "from": 172.06, "location": 2, "to": 174.13}, {"content": "店长 我只是能看到…", "from": 174.34, "location": 2, "to": 177.52}, {"content": "不对 我都打算去看脑子…", "from": 177.91, "location": 2, "to": 180.5}, {"content": "三角", "from": 180.5, "location": 2, "to": 181.45}, {"content": "这是命运", "from": 182.38, "location": 2, "to": 183.97}, {"content": "所以 店长", "from": 186.25, "location": 2, "to": 188.18}, {"content": "你说", "from": 188.62, "location": 2, "to": 189.24}, {"content": "请把三角交给我吧", "from": 190.87, "location": 2, "to": 192.84}, {"content": "我想要个助手", "from": 203.14, "location": 2, "to": 204.32}, {"content": "什么助手", "from": 204.99, "location": 2, "to": 205.64}, {"content": "刚才做的那件事", "from": 206.23, "location": 2, "to": 207.57}, {"content": "一个人做会很累", "from": 208.06, "location": 2, "to": 210.44}, {"content": "所以我能毫不夸张地说", "from": 211.08, "location": 2, "to": 214.63}, {"content": "遇到你这样有才能的人是命运", "from": 214.97, "location": 2, "to": 217.41}, {"content": "不骗你", "from": 217.92, "location": 2, "to": 218.71}, {"content": "别用奇怪的方式摸我", "from": 221.43, "location": 2, "to": 223.91}, {"content": "哪里奇怪了", "from": 224.48, "location": 2, "to": 225.12}, {"content": "我动不了", "from": 226.06, "location": 2, "to": 226.91}, {"content": "对 但我还没有碰到核心", "from": 227.36, "location": 2, "to": 230.42}, {"content": "核心？", "from": 231.16, "location": 2, "to": 231.97}, {"content": "类似灵魂的东西 你这个人的核心", "from": 232.18, "location": 2, "to": 235.8}, {"content": "想要我触碰吗", "from": 237.05, "location": 2, "to": 238.4}, {"content": "少给我开玩笑", "from": 238.88, "location": 2, "to": 240.13}, {"content": "你是叫冷川吧", "from": 240.86, "location": 2, "to": 242.66}, {"content": "是的", "from": 242.85, "location": 2, "to": 243.32}, {"content": "说实话 我很害怕", "from": 243.68, "location": 2, "to": 247.62}, {"content": "我摘下眼镜 也是为了不接近那东西", "from": 247.99, "location": 2, "to": 251.6}, {"content": "其他事物都很模糊 但只有那东西能看得很清楚", "from": 252.51, "location": 2, "to": 256.58}, {"content": "能分辨出来", "from": 256.89, "location": 2, "to": 258.02}, {"content": "能分辨出来就能逃跑", "from": 258.91, "location": 2, "to": 260.63}, {"content": "我害怕啊", "from": 261.72, "location": 2, "to": 262.9}, {"content": "放开我", "from": 264.0, "location": 2, "to": 264.72}, {"content": "三角", "from": 268.66, "location": 2, "to": 269.56}, {"content": "你只要和我在一起 就不会害怕了", "from": 270.19, "location": 2, "to": 273.64}, {"content": "我是HORI书店的山井", "from": 281.34, "location": 2, "to": 283.08}, {"content": "早安", "from": 283.25, "location": 2, "to": 284.68}, {"content": "是这样的", "from": 285.38, "location": 2, "to": 286.82}, {"content": "冷川先生拜托了我一件事", "from": 286.96, "location": 2, "to": 289.97}, {