to": 374.08}, {"content": "等等 快拔出来", "from": 374.92, "location": 2, "to": 377.54}, {"content": "放心 我会慢慢来", "from": 377.74, "location": 2, "to": 380.51}, {"content": "应该会很舒服才对 我就很舒服", "from": 381.01, "location": 2, "to": 384.14}, {"content": "居 居 居然没有勃起", "from": 384.63, "location": 2, "to": 387.8}, {"content": "因为舒服的不是身体", "from": 387.8, "location": 2, "to": 390.08}, {"content": "你真的很厉害", "from": 391.67, "location": 2, "to": 394.05}, {"content": "我 我说 那东西是不是在动？", "from": 394.98, "location": 2, "to": 398.34}, {"content": "因为我叫它过来了", "from": 399.59, "location": 2, "to": 401.57}, {"content": "为什么要做这种事啊", "from": 401.85, "location": 2, "to": 403.99}, {"content": "要是不进入能触碰到的距离 就不能把它扔掉了", "from": 404.24, "location": 2, "to": 407.01}, {"content": "要主动靠近吗", "from": 407.8, "location": 2, "to": 408.78}, {"content": "不要不要不要不要", "from": 409.37, "location": 2, "to": 410.96}, {"content": "绝对不要", "from": 410.96, "location": 2, "to": 412.28}, {"content": "为什么啊", "from": 412.28, "location": 2, "to": 412.98}, {"content": "你真能说", "from": 412.98, "location": 2, "to": 414.93}, {"content": "超可怕的啊", "from": 414.93, "location": 2, "to": 416.97}, {"content": "集中精神去感觉", "from": 417.06, "location": 2, "to": 419.33}, {"content": "就快碰到了", "from": 419.98, "location": 2, "to": 421.36}, {"content": "核心", "from": 422.62, "location": 2, "to": 423.36}, {"content": "害怕就闭上眼睛吧", "from": 427.6, "location": 2, "to": 429.66}, {"content": "能 能看见却不去看 才更可怕", "from": 431.25, "location": 2, "to": 436.2}, {"content": "你太棒了", "from": 437.0, "location": 2, "to": 438.75}, {"content": "扔掉了吗", "from": 458.04, "location": 2, "to": 459.37}, {"content": "扔掉了", "from": 459.84, "location": 2, "to": 461.16}, {"content": "你快看 干干净净", "from": 461.75, "location": 2, "to": 463.95}, {"content": "除 除灵居然这么色情 真的好吗", "from": 464.88, "location": 2, "to": 468.76}, {"content": "好 好舒…服", "from": 469.24, "location": 2, "to": 471.88}, {"content": "你知道吗", "from": 472.38, "location": 2, "to": 473.38}, {"content": "遇到灵异现象时 想些色情的事就好", "from":